As a parent, you are always concerned about your baby’s well being. With Vaccination, begins the journey of a healthy life. But this means multiple injections pain and repeated episodes of crying. 
With Combination Vaccinations like the 6-in-1 vaccinations, you can see your child smile a little more. 
6-in-1 vaccination combines 6 injections into a single shot and protects your child from 6 serious diseases.
Take charge of your baby’s health & keep a track of your baby’s vaccination card as it is their Health ka Passport.
To learn more visit https://www.myvaccinationhub.inbut/en/awareness-initiatives/6-in-1-vaccination 
Consult your pediatrician for more information & follow @myvaxihub for more content on disease/vaccination awareness.
